<p class="ql-align-justify">／在法律允许范围内，活动解释权归品牌所有／</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200922/acac1c5895244d24b9b5f660d141789a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>逃离广州1.5h，稻田温泉民宿小镇</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">-MI BU DAO XI WAN-</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>• 米埗稻喜湾民宿小镇 •</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200922/f2725c2176044c6ab13fc6987b34c696.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>• 一站式度假体验 • </strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200922/56ca76727f1f4859ae3e4bcc91847a1f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200922/f84fa09133f24893973fe3eec40a88f2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200922/5938dd3de59a4e8c9d222a4a011d830b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200922/8f75db82519e4d149e449326d9941e05.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200922/f12bbfcf887e4a1584cc3a5baa40518f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">国庆度个小假期，来这就够了，<strong>玩乐与美食兼得。</strong>不得不说这里<strong>超适合小姐姐专门来打卡拍照，</strong>每个角落都能出大片~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200922/ea0e1462401347709e079f32855dcffd.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>小苏打含"氡"稻田温泉，瑞士同款</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">-MI BU DAO XI WAN-</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>• 真温泉，全天无限泡 •</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200922/ff5499d05f6c4f1280e03fe744f961fa.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200922/f894ae705d6a4997bac33c341291af25.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>世界上极珍稀的两处含“氡”的弱碱性小苏打真温泉</strong>，富含30+种微量矿物质，<strong>一处在欧洲瑞士，另一处正是从化，</strong>被称为“温泉中的极品”。推开民宿的房门，下楼就能泡温泉。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200922/fea37cb7a03842da9411abafa91ffe07.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200922/08d01fd65c3b4ac686b9ad2d3d6542ae.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>______</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200922/b5aee61085cd4dfba53e872a72f2f549.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">18个原汤和养生温泉池，一边泡一边感受<strong>“天然的精华水”</strong>对皮肤的滋养，<strong>泡完后的肌肤仿佛喝饱了水，</strong>难怪女孩子对小苏打温泉趋之若鹜。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>■ 11:00am</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200922/729989eade1c46209ff014bcc523585d.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200922/be8f366859a44ae39d5355b3fcfceef8.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>背靠远处仙雾缭绕的凤凰群山</strong>，感受着穿过稻田的清风吹拂在脸上，置身于<strong>大自然的户外环境中泡着温泉，</strong>这才是假期该有的样子啊，好治愈~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200922/d5905ba505b24e539aee2177a358e945.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200922/3e54b78672be425ea34c6ab851559051.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">除了原汤池，这里还有<strong>玫瑰池、柠檬池、淘米池、鸳鸯池等9池养生温泉</strong>，和小姐妹一人泡一个池，谈天说地，时光仿佛都慢了下来。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200922/9a886124262d4075b594b75bd8dfb8d7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200922/b77d7bc049ea4a638de35c8c83873f9d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200922/9a82de6d048d4bf4aaa0a37d6ab57460.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200922/1193984b98974f1cba7a1d6ec52b8af7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">温泉水和周边的环境自然融为一体，伴随着粼粼浮动的波光倒影，<strong>相机镜头也一本满足~</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>■ 20:00pm</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200922/9c57d129532949fbaf806baa9670bd06.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200922/4ccfde9ca4d64177878aba330b08e840.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">温泉中心营业到23:00，<strong>吃完晚餐休息一下，又可以下水啦~</strong>晚上的温泉池被柔和的彩光包围，别有一番感觉。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200922/d91b7b2978e64c37a24b942a23ac82e2.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200922/dd51a6e0267c42c8bd88a5faa6d33f39.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200922/0410d9bd30044d139809ab4282890c8c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200922/a2332d36e8b94156a754a6f2e8f838a9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">在四周一片朦胧的水雾中，<strong>紧绷的神经和疲惫的身体逐渐松弛下来，</strong>回房直接洗个澡倒头就睡到天亮~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>• 自带梦幻飘雪池 •</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200922/c11b28bc42d8464598afda65d8abfda5.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200922/df0d054946874b59b07a4ab05f466dcf.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200922/f92f49daa0214fd99a210796cefdef03.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">● ● ●</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200922/55df8384548741b19949983f6f149740.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">冬天还有少女心满满的造雪机！这次广州人不用出省也能看雪了！飘落的“雪花”在掌心融化，<strong>仿佛置身于北海道的飘雪池，</strong>冰火两重天，<strong>浪漫又梦幻~</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>• 360°无边恒温泳池 •</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200922/7dc0f29325f8444f90b792ed061ea636.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">///</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200922/fda4a33606f648f0b3402ac04bb6111b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">在无边的泳池里，一年四季都能无视温度畅泳。趴在泳池边上一边<strong>享受着日光浴，</strong>一边看着飞过的群鸟，<strong>傍晚还能直接观赏夕阳红霞！</strong>所有的烦恼此刻统统被抛诸脑后...</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200922/e210254318c243ff9f9480cae0a42131.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">×××</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200922/fb1915abb6c5466fbd20fe21da78a318.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200922/c7f607b2796e42ce9df6bc7bd7a323e0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">泳池的水不深，<strong>旱鸭子也可以下水凹一套泳池写真大片。</strong>如果男朋友这次还不能把你拍好看的话，真的得换一个了！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200922/1dd6c4a6f019488fb6e0e4bef8d1aa21.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>穿梭稻田小火车 x 网红打卡点</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">-MI BU DAO XI WAN-</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>• 复古仿蒸汽小火车 •</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200922/a520d1308ada4d38855d4de03ae9e259.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200922/2705ef252a5240198cdf4062e659fd50.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200922/44a969802ced43c8b20b9ac75d12b359.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">足足35亩的碧绿稻田，和周边的森林大山融为一体，<strong>仿佛世外桃源一般。</strong>红色的复古仿蒸汽小火车，“呼哧呼哧”地穿梭在稻田间，<strong>风吹稻浪，童趣又惬意。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200922/103fac358e7f42b1a3d6e3fa31efa30d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200922/a4d32645d4934a65ba5a62a3729770dc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">等到冬天降临，<strong>稻田变得满眼金黄，更如诗般浪漫了呢。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>• 热门打卡点《拍照指南》•</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>■ 小火车站台</strong></p>
